# Objective

Create a user-friendly guide that explains how to complete a common task within a software application. The guide should use clear language, logical organization, and step-by-step instructions suitable for non-technical users.

---

# Scenario

A new user has just created an account on a cloud storage platform and wants to upload their first file.

